article.description: — Samage Teel scored 18 points to help Presbyterian defeat Charleston Southern 72-65 on Saturday.
article.headline: Teel scores 18, guides Presbyterian over Charleston Southern 72-65
article.linkText: Teel scores 18, guides Presbyterian over Charleston Southern 72-65
article.story: CLINTON, S.C. -- — Samage Teel scored 18 points to help Presbyterian defeat Charleston Southern 72-65 on Saturday. Teel added six rebounds for the Blue Hose (14-17, 6-10 Big South Conference). Trevon Reddish had 16 points on 6-for-6 shooting. Kobe Stewart made 6 of 9 shots and scored 15. A'lahn Sumler led the way for the Buccaneers (10-19, 6-10) with 23 points. Taje' Kelly added 14 points. RJ Johnson had 11 points and eight assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
